### USER REGISTRATION
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "anurag",
  "lastname": "reddy",
  "email": "anurag@email.com",
  "password": "author@123",
  "profileImageUrl": "http://example.com/avatar/user.png"
}

### USER REGISTRATION (SECOND USER)
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "purushotham",
  "lastName": "reddy",
  "email": "SPR@email.com",
  "password": "user@123",
  "profileImageUrl": "http://example.com/avatar/user.png"
}

### USER AUTHENTICATION (LOGIN)
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "anurag@email.com",
  "password": "author@123",
  "role": "USER"
}

### USER AUTHENTICATION (LOGIN SECOND USER)
POST http://localhost:4000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "SPR@email.com",
  "password": "user@123"
}

### GET ALL USERS
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/users

### GET ALL ARTICLES
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/articles

### GET ARTICLES BY AUTHOR ID
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/articles/author/69896f3ae6cc1dc714dfc5d0

### COMMENT BY USER
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "articleId": "69897c57cd1ce69831ca7bba",
  "userId": "69899bcfceaa6b354900e337",
  "comment": "This is a great article"
}

