### CREATE ARTICLE
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Researching AI djshfjdskfkjsdhfjksdhfjhskjdffnmd",
  "category": "Backend AI",
  "content": "This article explains AI ands backend research."
}


### GET ARTICLES BY AUTHOR
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/author/69ae8b55b672900e29019f07



### UPDATE ARTICLE
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69ae88fbb672900e29019efb
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updating Example",
  "category": "Vehicle",
  "content": "Volvo car is strong"
}
### DELETE ARTICLE
DELETE http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69ae88fbb672900e29019efb

### ADMIN LOGIN
POST http://localhost:4000/admin-api/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@email.com",
  "password": "admin@123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### ADMIN READ ARTICLES BY AUTHOR
GET http://localhost:4000/admin-api/articles/author/69896f3ae6cc1dc714dfc5d0

### BLOCK USER
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users/block/69896f29e6cc1dc714dfc5cb

### UNBLOCK USER
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users/unblock/69896f29e6cc1dc714dfc5cb

